        "badge": "OUR STORY",
        "heading": "Built from the Ground Up",
        "text": "<p>Street Rulz Football was born from a simple belief — that the Gold Coast deserves a world-class small-sided football facility where community, culture, and competition come together.</p><p>What started as a family vision has grown into 7 premium enclosed pitches at Tallebudgera, built with FIFA Grade 3 artificial turf and designed for players of every level. From casual kick-abouts to competitive leagues, birthday parties to junior academies — Rulz is where street culture meets elite football.</p><p>We're a family-run business, and that's by design. Every decision we make is driven by a genuine love for the game and a commitment to the community we serve.</p>",
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/IMG_0953_2.jpg",
        "image_alt": "Street Rulz Football facility at Tallebudgera",
